an class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 11, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104rlu1665702783545.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rlu1665702783545.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rlu1665702783545.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"rlu1665702783545\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"rlu1665702783545___sqrt_290273\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Returns the square root of X.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"rlu1665702783545__topic_d89630e1_d89631e1_d89632e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rlu1665702783545__p_d89633e1_d89634e1_d89635e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$sqrt</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">X</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rlu1665702783545__topic_d59632e1_d59633e1_d59634e1_d59635e1_d59636e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d682567e74\">\n                       \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rlu1665702783545__p_d89639e1_d89640e1_d89641e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">X</var>—positive numeric constant, or a field (or indirect reference to a field), variable, function, or expression that evaluates to a positive numeric value.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rlu1665702783545__topic_d59637e1_d59638e1_d59639e1_d59640e1_d59641e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d682567e86\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rlu1665702783545__p_d89645e1_d89646e1_d89647e1\">Square root of <var class=\"keyword varname\">X</var>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rlu1665702783545__p_d89648e1_d89649e1_d89650e1\">If an error occurs, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> contains a negative value that identifies the exact error.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"rlu1665702783545__table_d9698e1_d9699e1_d9700e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Values of<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span>Commonly Returned Following<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$sqrt</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rlu1665702783545__table_d9698e1_d9699e1_d9700e1__entry__1\">\n Value \n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rlu1665702783545__table_d9698e1_d9699e1_d9700e1__entry__2\">\n Error constant\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rlu1665702783545__table_d9698e1_d9699e1_d9700e1__entry__3\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rlu1665702783545__table_d9698e1_d9699e1_d9700e1__entry__1\">\n -1204\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rlu1665702783545__table_d9698e1_d9699e1_d9700e1__entry__2\">\n &lt;UPROCERR_NEGATIVE&gt;\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rlu1665702783545__table_d9698e1_d9699e1_d9700e1__entry__3\">\n Negative value not allowed.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rlu1665702783545__topic_d59642e1_d59643e1_d59644e1_d59645e1_d59646e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d682567e155\">\n                       \n Use\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rlu1665702783545__p_d89654e1_d89655e1_d89656e1\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rlu1665702783545__section_x1q_nx3_1cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d682567e165\">Example: Using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$sqrt</span></h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">The following example computes the square root of 0.5.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"rlu1665702783545__pre_xg1_4x3_1cc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">vRoot = $sqrt(1/2)\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531672\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531672\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$sqrt Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 11, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Returns the square root of X. $sqrt ( X ) Parameters X —positive numeric constant, or a field (or indirect reference to a field), variable, function, or expression that evaluates to a positive numeric value. Return Values Square root of X If an error occurs, $procerror contains a negative value that identifies the exact error. Table 1. Values of $procerror Commonly Returned Following $sqrt Value Error constant Meaning -1204 <UPROCERR_NEGATIVE> Negative value not allowed. Use Allowed in all component types. Example: Using $sqrt The following example computes the square root of 0.5. vRoot = $sqrt(1/2) Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}